= Instruction =

1. install some ruby libraries
 - openssl
 - json
 - prowl (rubygems)

2. setup config.yml

3. run twiprowl


= config.yml =

Prowl:
 APIKey: <the Prowl API Key>

Accounts:
 -
  Application: <application name (optional)> 
  User: <Twitter username>
  Pass: <Twitter Password>
  Mentions: <true|false> # Mentions
  MentionsCount: <limit to get new mentions (int)>
  MentionsInterval: <check interval (min)>
  Direct: <true|false> # Direct Message
  DirectCount: <limit to get new DirectMessage (int)>
  DirectInterval: <check interval (min)>
  Debug: <true|false> # debug outputs
 - 
  <Other account config here>
